      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 80: 🔴 Critical Issues - The text binding calls `MessagesAdapter.parseOriginalMessage()` every time `showOriginal` is true and `ParsedOriginalBody.length \u003d\u003d\u003d 0`. Because parsing is asynchronous and the model role is empty until completion, repeated binding reevaluations can enqueue duplicate parse jobs for the same message. Add an in-flight flag/role, or cache parse requests per message before starting another parse.\n```suggestion\nif (showOriginal \u0026\u0026 isPluginOverwrite) {\n    if (OriginalBody !\u003d\u003d \"\" \u0026\u0026 ParsedOriginalBody.length \u003d\u003d\u003d 0 \u0026\u0026 !originalParseRequested) {\n        originalParseRequested \u003d true;\n        MessagesAdapter.parseOriginalMessage(Id, OriginalBody, rootDelegate.colorUrl, bubble.color);\n    }\n    return ParsedOriginalBody;\n}\n```",
