      "message": "Line 50: 🟡 Suggestions - `buildStyledHtml()` now contains the shared parsing logic but still uses the instance `htmlParser_` from worker-thread tasks. The current pool size of 1 limits concurrency, but this helper is not self-contained and can become unsafe if the pool size changes or another caller uses it concurrently. Prefer a parser instance local to the worker/helper, or document/enforce that all calls are serialized.\n```suggestion\nHtmlParser htmlParser;\nhtmlParser.parseHtmlString(html);\nauto tagsMap \u003d htmlParser.getTagsNodes({TidyTag_A, TidyTag_DEL, TidyTag_PRE});\n```",
